      "title": "Charges filed against Pakistan's former prime minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Pakistani police have filed charges against former Prime Minister Imran Khan for violating anti-terror laws, local authorities said.",
        "The move came after Khan was accused of threatening a member of the judiciary and police officers."
